title: Crypto Firm BitGo Pares Gains in Debut After $212.8 Million IPO
description: BitGo Holdings Inc. shares pared an initial gain to end 3.8% above the IPO price, after the crypto firm and some of its backers raised $212.8 million in a US initial public offering.
